FREE MONEY ALERT: I’m always looking for ways to say thank you for supporting my content. Without your support I wouldn’t have access to high stakes live stream games which are so important for a poker player in today’s poker climate. Which is why it feels appropriate to give away freerolls to my action in these live stream games as a way to say thank you. The problem is that traditionally people will ask for likes, retweets, or follows as a way to enter the drawing. But that doesn’t accomplish the goal of thanking the people that support me the most. To me, the best way to say thank you is by giving away freeroll pieces to people that buy merch. These are the people that are truly supporting me. So from here on out. Every single time I play on a live stream. I’m going to give away a small percentage of my action in these high stakes games. Games that I will buy up to $50K in so it potentially means a lot of free money. The morning of every live stream, I’ll enter everyone who purchased merch between the previous live stream and the current live stream in to a random drawing. My next live stream will likely be on Thursday. Link to my merch is in my bio or you can just go to Johnnievibes.com if you want a chance at a piece of the action. 🚀
